  <brief_title>Effect of Tranexamic Acid on Prevention of Recurrence of Hemoptysis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Tranexamic Acid on Prevention of Recurrence of Hemoptysis: Multicenter, Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind Phase 3 Trial</official_title>
