  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hemoptysis is one of the serious complication of many pulmonary diseases. Upto now, there is
      no proven medical treatment in recurrence of hemoptysis. The investigators will conduct a
      randomized, placebo controlled trial of tranexamic acid, which can reduce the recurrence of
      hemoptysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
